rification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestSanitizeName -v`\n33: \n34: - [x] **T1.4**: Implement `KubernetesProvider._ensure_namespace` helper\n35:   - Purpose: Ensure target namespace exists, create if 404\n36:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:321-336`\n37:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestEnsureNamespace -v`\n38: \n39: - [x] **T1.5**: Implement `KubernetesProvider._create_deployment` private method\n40:   - Purpose: Create Deployment with env vars, entrypoint, replicas\n41:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:88-143`\n42:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestCreateDeployment -v`\n43: \n44: - [x] **T1.6**: Implement `KubernetesProvider._patch_deployment` private method\n45:   - Purpose: Patch existing Deployment on 409 conflict\n46:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:145-192`\n47:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestCreateDeployment::test_create_deployment_with_env_vars -v`\n48: \n49: - [x] **T1.7**: Implement `KubernetesProvider._create_service` private method\n50:   - Purpose: Create/patch NodePort Service with optional fixed node_port\n51:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:194-240`\n52:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestCreateService -v`\n53: \n54: - [x] **T1.8**: Implement `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready` method\n55:   - Purpose: Poll deployment until available_replicas == replicas or timeout\n56:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:242-258`\n57:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestWaitForDeploymentReady -v`\n58: \n59: - [x] **T1.9**: Implement `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent` orchestrator method\n60:   - Purpose: Create Deployment + Service, wait for readiness, return deployment info\n61:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:38-86`\n62:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestDeployAgent -v`\n63: \n64: - [x] **T1.10**: Implement `KubernetesProvider.get_agent_status` method\n65:   - Purpose: Get Deployment and Service status from Kubernetes\n66:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:260-292`\n67:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestGetAgentStatus -v`\n68: \n69: - [x] **T1.11**: Implement `KubernetesProvider.delete_agent` method\n70:   - Purpose: Delete Deployment and Service, ignore 404 errors\n71:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py:294-319`\n72:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestDeleteAgent -v`\n73: \n74: ### Phase 2: AgentCubeProvider Implementation (ST-2)\n75: \n76: - [x] **T2.1**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider.__init__` with namespace, verbose, kubeconfig params\n77:   - Purpose: Initialize provider with CustomObjectsApi for CR management\n78:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:18-37`\n79:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestAgentCubeProviderInit -v`\n80: \n81: - [x] **T2.2**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider` constants (CR_GROUP, CR_VERSION, CR_PLURAL, timeouts)\n82:   - Purpose: Define AgentRuntime CRD constants and default timeouts\n83:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:11-16`\n84:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestConstants -v`\n85: \n86: - [x] **T2.3**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider._sanitize_name` helper\n87:   - Purpose: Sanitize agent names for AgentRuntime CR naming (same logic as K8sProvider)\n88:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:185-190`\n89:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestSanitizeName -v`\n90: \n91: - [x] **T2.4**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider._ensure_namespace` helper\n92:   - Purpose: Ensure target namespace exists for CR deployment\n93:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:169-183`\n94:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestEnsureNamespace -v`\n95: \n96: - [x] **T2.5**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime` method\n97:   - Purpose: Create/Patch AgentRuntime CR with readiness probe, env vars, imagePullSecrets\n98:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:39-130`\n99:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestDeployAgentRuntime -v`\n100: \n101: - [x] **T2.6**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider.get_agent_runtime` method\n102:   - Purpose: Get AgentRuntime CR object from Kubernetes, return None if 404\n103:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:132-148`\n104:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestGetAgentRuntime -v`\n105: \n106: - [x] **T2.7**: Implement `AgentCubeProvider.delete_agent_runtime` method\n107:   - Purpose: Delete AgentRuntime CR, return not_found reason if 404\n108:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py:150-167`\n109:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py::TestDeleteAgentRuntime -v`\n110: \n111: ### Phase 3: KubernetesProvider Unit Tests (ST-3)\n112: \n113: - [x] **T3.1**: Test KubernetesProvider init with default namespace\n114:   - Purpose: Verify default namespace is \"default\"\n115:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:9-14`\n116:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestKubernetesProviderInit::test_init_default_namespace -v`\n117: \n118: - [x] **T3.2**: Test KubernetesProvider init with custom namespace\n119:   - Purpose: Verify custom namespace is set correctly\n120:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:16-21`\n121:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestKubernetesProviderInit::test_init_custom_namespace -v`\n122: \n123: - [x] **T3.3**: Test KubernetesProvider init with verbose flag\n124:   - Purpose: Verify verbose flag is stored\n125:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:23-28`\n126:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestKubernetesProviderInit::test_init_verbose -v`\n127: \n128: - [x] **T3.4**: Test _sanitize_name lowercase conversion\n129:   - Purpose: Verify name is lowercased\n130:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:32-38`\n131:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestSanitizeName::test_sanitize_name_lowercase -v`\n132: \n133: - [x] **T3.5**: Test _sanitize_name replace non-alphanumeric\n134:   - Purpose: Verify non-alphanumeric chars replaced with dash\n135:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:40-46`\n136:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestSanitizeName::test_sanitize_name_replace_non_alphanumeric -v`\n137: \n138: - [x] **T3.6**: Test _sanitize_name truncate to 63 chars\n139:   - Purpose: Verify Kubernetes name length limit enforced\n140:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:48-55`\n141:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestSanitizeName::test_sanitize_name_truncate_to_63_chars -v`\n142: \n143: - [x] **T3.7**: Test _sanitize_name strip dashes\n144:   - Purpose: Verify leading/trailing dashes stripped\n145:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:57-63`\n146:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestSanitizeName::test_sanitize_name_strip_dashes -v`\n147: \n148: - [x] **T3.8**: Test _sanitize_name empty string returns \"default\"\n149:   - Purpose: Verify empty name defaults to \"default\"\n150:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:65-71`\n151:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestSanitizeName::test_sanitize_name_empty_string -v`\n152: \n153: - [x] **T3.9**: Test _sanitize_name all special chars returns \"default\"\n154:   - Purpose: Verify all-special input defaults to \"default\"\n155:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:73-79`\n156:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestSanitizeName::test_sanitize_name_all_special_chars -v`\n157: \n158: - [x] **T3.10**: Test _ensure_namespace when exists\n159:   - Purpose: Verify namespace check succeeds when exists\n160:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:82-94`\n161:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestEnsureNamespace::test_ensure_namespace_exists -v`\n162: \n163: - [x] **T3.11**: Test _ensure_namespace creates when not exists\n164:   - Purpose: Verify namespace created on 404\n165:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:96-109`\n166:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestEnsureNamespace::test_ensure_namespace_creates_if_not_exists -v`\n167: \n168: - [x] **T3.12**: Test _create_deployment basic\n169:   - Purpose: Verify Deployment created with required fields\n170:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:113-133`\n171:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestCreateDeployment::test_create_deployment_basic -v`\n172: \n173: - [x] **T3.13**: Test _create_deployment with env vars\n174:   - Purpose: Verify env vars added to Deployment spec\n175:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:135-157`\n176:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestCreateDeployment::test_create_deployment_with_env_vars -v`\n177: \n178: - [x] **T3.14**: Test _create_deployment with entrypoint\n179:   - Purpose: Verify command set from entrypoint string\n180:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:159-181`\n181:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestCreateDeployment::test_create_deployment_with_entrypoint -v`\n182: \n183: - [x] **T3.15**: Test _create_service basic\n184:   - Purpose: Verify NodePort Service created\n185:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py:185-200`\n186:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py::TestCreateService::test_create_service_basic -v`\n187: \n188: - [x] **T3.16**: Test _create_service with fixed no