time.py cmd/cli/tests/test_status_runtime.py -v` |\n554: | Phase 7 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -k \"k8s_provider or agentcube_provider or publish_runtime or invoke_runtime or status_runtime\" -v` |\n555: | All Tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v` |\n556: \n557: ---\n558: \n559: ## Acceptance Criteria\n560: \n561: - [x] `KubernetesProvider` class implemented with all API methods\n562: - [x] `KubernetesProvider.NODE_PORT_MIN` = 30000, `NODE_PORT_MAX` = 32767\n563: - [x] `KubernetesProvider.DEFAULT_TIMEOUT` = 120 seconds\n564: - [x] `KubernetesProvider._sanitize_name` follows Kubernetes naming conventions\n565: - [x] `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent` creates Deployment + NodePort Service\n566: - [x] `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready` polls until ready or timeout\n567: - [x] `KubernetesProvider.get_agent_status` returns deployment and service status\n568: - [x] `KubernetesProvider.delete_agent` deletes Deployment and Service\n569: - [x] `AgentCubeProvider` class implemented with CR methods\n570: - [x] `AgentCubeProvider.CR_GROUP` = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n571: - [x] `AgentCubeProvider.CR_VERSION` = \"v1alpha1\", `CR_PLURAL` = \"agentruntimes\"\n572: - [x] `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime` creates AgentRuntime CR\n573: - [x] `AgentCubeProvider.get_agent_runtime` returns CR or None on 404\n574: - [x] `AgentCubeProvider.delete_agent_runtime` deletes CR with not_found handling\n575: - [x] `PublishRuntime` integrates both providers with provider selection\n576: - [x] `InvokeRuntime` integrates both providers with endpoint rewrite for AgentRuntime\n577: - [x] `StatusRuntime` integrates both providers with status retrieval\n578: - [x] All 23 KubernetesProvider unit tests pass\n579: - [x] All 20 AgentCubeProvider unit tests pass\n580: - [x] All 21 Runtime integration tests pass\n581: - [x] `KubernetesProvider` and `AgentCubeProvider` exported from services package\n582: \n583: ---\n584: \n585: ## File Changes Summary\n586: \n587: | File | Action | Lines | Description |\n588: |------|--------|-------|-------------|\n589: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | Created | 342 | KubernetesProvider implementation |\n590: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | Created | 190 | AgentCubeProvider implementation |\n591: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_k8s_provider.py` | Created | 373 | KubernetesProvider unit tests |\n592: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_agentcube_provider.py` | Created | 446 | AgentCubeProvider unit tests |\n593: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | Modified | 271 | Added provider integration |\n594: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | Modified | 117 | Added provider integration |\n595: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | Modified | 157 | Added provider integration |\n596: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_publish_runtime.py` | Created | 431 | PublishRuntime tests |\n597: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_invoke_runtime.py` | Created | 402 | InvokeRuntime tests |\n598: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_status_runtime.py` | Created | 506 | StatusRuntime tests |\n599: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Modified | 8 | Export providers |\n600: \n601: ---\n602: \n603: ## Implementation Notes\n604: \n605: ### KubernetesProvider Key Features\n606: \n607: - **NodePort Service**: Creates NodePort type Service for external access\n608: - **Deployment Management**: Creates/patches Deployments with env vars and entrypoint\n609: - **Readiness Waiting**: Polls deployment status with configurable timeout\n610: - **Error Handling**: Handles 409 (conflict) by patching, ignores 404 on delete\n611: \n612: ### AgentCubeProvider Key Features\n613: \n614: - **Custom Resource**: Uses CustomObjectsApi for AgentRuntime CR\n615: - **CRD Constants**: Defines group, version, plural for AgentRuntime CRD\n616: - **Readiness Probe**: Configures HTTP readiness probe with defaults\n617: - **ImagePullSecrets**: Sets default-secret for image registry auth\n618: \n619: ### Provider Selection Pattern\n620: \n621: ```python\n622: if provider == \"k8s\":\n623:     from agentcube.services.k8s_provider import KubernetesProvider\n624:     self._k8s_provider = KubernetesProvider(verbose=verbose)\n625: elif provider == \"agentcube\":\n626:     from agentcube.services.agentcube_provider import AgentCubeProvider\n627:     self._agentcube_provider = AgentCubeProvider(verbose=verbose)\n628: else:\n629:     raise ValueError(f\"Invalid provider: {provider}. Must be 'agentcube' or 'k8s'\")\n630: ```\n631: \n632: ### AgentRuntime Endpoint Rewrite\n633: \n634: For AgentRuntime CR invocations, the endpoint URL is rewritten:\n635: ```\n636: Original: http://api-server.example.com\n637: Rewritten: http://api-server.example.com/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{name}/invocations/\n638: ```\n639: \n640: ---\n641: \n642: ## Implementation Timeline\n643: \n644: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n645: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n646: | Phase 1: KubernetesProvider | T1.1-T1.11 | Done | 100% |\n647: | Phase 2: AgentCubeProvider | T2.1-T2.7 | Done | 100% |\n648: | Phase 3: K8s Tests | T3.1-T3.23 | Done | 100% |\n649: | Phase 4: AgentCube Tests | T4.1-T4.20 | Done | 100% |\n650: | Phase 5: Runtime Integration | T5.1-T5.8 | Done | 100% |\n651: | Phase 6: Runtime Tests | T6.1-T6.21 | Done | 100% |\n652: | Phase 7: Package Export | T7.1-T7.4 | Done | 100% |\n653: \n654: **Total Progress: 100% Complete (73/73 tasks)**\n655: \n656: ---\n657: \n658: ## References\n659: \n660: - Design: `changes/AR-026/design.md`\n661: - cli-toolkit/design.md — CLI toolkit architecture\n662: - cli-toolkit/spec.md — CLI specification\n\n(End of file - total 662 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-026 — K8s/AgentCube Provider Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-026 — K8s/AgentCube Provider |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: KubernetesProvider Implementation 